column7: Esther Nish - Francine Niyonsaba (Fire Cine) [Official Audio]
column8:
Burundian athlete Niyonsaba Francine has just written the lines of history in her own way. Selected for the Tokyo Olympics which took place from July 23 to August 8, 2021 in Japan, she got disqualified which she described as unfair.

In the process, she goes on to competitions which she all wins with one notable exception. In fact, on Tuesday September 14, 2021 at the Boris Hanzekovic Memorial, Francine won the 2000m competition and broke the world record. Burundians all over the world are celebrating this courageous woman.

Esther Nish went quickly into studio to pay a tribute to this brave woman. In a song. Enjoy it.

column8:
Esther Nish, one of the best famous female artists all the way from Burundi decided to write a song that she titled 'Ntunkologe'. It means: 'Don't disturb my mood'.
The song is feminist. In fact, after days being a good woman at home, an evening, she decided to send a message to her man that she will be having fun with friends. It went well. The rest of the story is in this clip.

column8:
Official Music Video of "NOPFA" 
performed by Double Jay and Kirikou Akili

Starring: Michael Sengazi
Video Director: John Elarts 
Prod. by Endo Mike The Machine

Nopfa lyrics:
_

Vers.1 : Tutaramenyana nari umuhungu yitonda/
Kuva tubaye abajama raba ndateye agahinda/

Wahinduye vyinshi kuri jewe my friend..../
Oya nukuri jewe numva ngira mpfe..../

Niwe wanyigije ku draga/
Abana nkuranya ijoro numutaga/
Uzohava unta mukaga/
Ubu mbonye umukobwa amatwi arashinga/

Tunywa inzoga nyinshi ntitwigerera/
Maze iminsi ntaboneka no muhira/
Mugenzi wanje uzohava unkwegera/ x2
............My friend

__

Chorus: Nokwishinga nopfa, nokwishinga nopfa 
Ego ndabizi ko urumugenzi ariko nokwishinga nopfa 
No no no no ....(Nopfa )  no no no no no ........(Nopfa) 
 
Bridge : Mmmmh Oooh my friend  dupunguze ama party iiiish My best friend tureke kwama muri  party.....

Vers.2 : Niwe wanyigije kunywa ama biya/
Niwe wanyigishije ku baya/
Raba nsigaye kumisaya/
Ndiraba mukiyo nkigaya/
Ndabembeya nsigaye ni vampaya/ (vampire)
Mambo mbaya burimunsi  mukirori ni faya/ (Fire )

Mbega ayo mafaranga uyakurahe Eeeeh.../
Mbega mugenzi wanje wewe ukorahe..../

Turarengeje vyoba vyiza dupunguje/
Erega ni danger kwama twiteretse ibidaje/

Tunywa inzoga nyinshi............

Chorus : ................


Vers.3: Oooh my friend, Ooh my friend 
Mbega turiko tuganahe Ooh my friend 
Ooh my friend, Ooh my friend tugire twikebuke nukuri Ooh my friend

Wamumbwira ngo sinibane/ ngubuzima nibuto cane/ ariko mbonaringorane tugire twikebuke twarengeje cane/ 
Kuryabana , kuryabana/ twabigizumugenzo turarengeje sana/ kugendana/ dusohokana / vyambereyikibazo nubwo nkukunda sana.

 Ephesians 3:20 : Now to him who by the power at work within in us is able to do far more abundantly than all that we ask or think

Aphesis (imbabazi) zatumye nemerwa ntaruwo kwemera (x2)

column7: Sat B, Best Life Music, Belle 9ice, Clementine Kavy & Bain Turo - 50-100 Amabuno (Officia Video)
column8:
EMPIRE AVENUEâ€™S ARTISTS release the video of  "50-100 (Amabuno)"
Sat-B, Best Life Music, Belle 9ice, Clementine Kavy and Bain Turo have just collaborated on a new song called "50-100 (Amabuno)". 
 
If, like many, you're wondering why there are so many artists on just one song, it's because these artists all belong to the same label, EMPIRE AVENUE. However, having them all at the same joint is certainly a first and for that, "50-100 (Amabuno)" made history.
Video directed by Kent-P, shot in Burundi
One of Burundianâ€™s biggest record label has hit the headlines yet again. This time round, the Buja Flava stars has merged together with a collabo that is currently ruling the music charts dubbed 50-100 (Amabuno).
Produced by Amir.
Enjoy the Video.

column7: Sat-B - African Gal (Official Video)
column8:
Kora Entertainment present AFRICAN GAL, East Africa's Artist Sat-B drops her latest single African Gal. This enchanting love song was produced by Rwandan producer Pacento. this song is a feel good guaranteed anthem. Accompanied by visuals directed by Meddie Menz from Uganda,the video was shooted in Kampala and Kigali, this sexy love song is another testimony of the increase in quality productions from Burundi and a definite new fan favorite for Sat-B fans. 
Sat-B considered influential among his fans, and is said to be the most loved Burundian artist at the moment. LEVEL UP with Vusi Nova https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PH0wg4e91Ak 

#Africori #TheBestInAfricanMusic #BestOfAfrica

column8:
The wait is over now, Burundian artist SAT-B premieres the most anticipated song titled No Love after the success of his previously smash tune FeelLove, that till now leads the playlists on most Burundian medias.

This song was produced by the famous burundian producer Amir Pro and the talented tanzanian producer Yogo Beat,  the video was shot and directed by Joowzey from Tanzania LEVEL UP with Vusi Nova https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PH0wg4e91Ak

column7: Sat B, Best Life Music, Belle 9ice, Clementine Kavy and Bain Turo - 50-100 (Amabuno) [Audio]
column8:
EMPIRE AVENUEâ€™S ARTISTS COLLABORATE ON "50-100 (Amabuno)"
Sat-B, Best Life Music, Belle 9ice, Clementine Kavy and Bain Turo have just collaborated on a new song called "50-100 (Amabuno)". 
All the artiste of Empire Avenue was being promoted on social media for a week in sharing the hashtag #Amabuno.
 
If, like many, you're wondering why there are so many artists on just one song, it's because these artists all belong to the same label, EMPIRE AVENUE. However, having them all at the same joint is certainly a first and for that, "50-100 (Amabuno)" made history.
One of Burundianâ€™s biggest record label has hit the headlines yet again. This time round, the Buja Flava stars has merged together with a collabo that is currently ruling the music charts dubbed 50-100 (Amabuno).
Produced by Amir.
Enjoy it.

amarira kumushaha aruzuranye 
sinzorya akarenz' umuryango 
ngapfana ukwizera n'ukuzeruka 
ngapfana agahinda n'umubabaro 
barundi mwe.

column7: B FACE - UMWANA MU MURYANGO (Official Music Video)
column8:
B FACE releases the official Video of The UMWANA MU MURYANGO single.
The song speaks about a Project realized by IRC in Burundi in partnership with Dutabarane under the leadership of the Ministry of National Solidarity, Social Affairs, Human Rights and Gender through its Direction for Children and Family, with a funding from the European Union. The UMMU project contributed to the implementation of the National Child Protection Policy in Burundi (PNPE), and the National Strategy for Alternative Care of Children in Burundi (SNPCAEB).
#ircburundi, #dutabarane

column7: SIKO YARI -B FACE (OFFICIAL AUDIO)
column8:
Finally ,It's out now.
SIKO YARI -B FACE  feat. YVETTE (OFFICIAL AUDIO)
produced by Amir Pro

LYRICS

Oohhh Eehh
Eehh

[Yvette]
Siko yari ahubwo niko yabaye
Yavutse nk'abandi arira agahozwa
BwaraKeye bucana ayandi
Aho yariraha barabahamba
Kiramwa kira kandi cagutse
Yabaye impfuvyi atabishaka

[B Face]
Inyamaswa ntindi ivyara uruhigi
Gwaramutse
Birababaje kubona uvuka aho vyuzuye
Bikarangira womotse Niko yabaye
Iyo mpfuvyi siko yavutse
Murindakiji hama bakajya yicaye
Ibyo bamusigiye navyo barasahuye
Agizengo arabaza avuga bamuzibiye
Abicike gute ko nurya womuvugiye
Ari mubamuriye
Aragwara akirwaza agakizwa n'ibihe
Kwataharira yaha yakwivuza hehe
Ntiyiga nkabandi avuga uti nivyahe..
Ushobora kwibaza uti kuki abaye gutya
Kandi yavutse nk'abandi
Arasonza akigunga kandi yataragera
Ararira akayaha abatayakira
Nuwo yituye ntihagira icyo amumarira
Nuwo yituye ntihagira icyo amumarira
Iminsi yose akama ari n'amarira
Bararya bagahaga bakaryama heza
Nawe ubwiwe ahaze umuyaga
Akamana ibibazo ahari ishavu n'iniga
Agenze ngo ashize umujinya
Agatsira ntashira akagumya ari ukwidoda
Abyuka yiruka akakimaza amaguru
Atagira iyo aja rikarinda rirenga
Siko yavutse niho yabonye yisanga

[Yvette]

Siko yari ahubwo niko yabaye
Yavutse nk'abandi arira agahozwa
Bwarakeye bucana ayandi
Aho yariraha barabahamba
Kiramwa kira kandi cagutse
Yabaye impfubyi atabishaka

[B Face]

Umwana wibarabara
Imbere arironderera
Numvise ibitanderera ahubwo
Ubu mutahura
Nawe yavyisanzemo
Hanyuma aratangara
Kuba impfuvyi birababaza
Kandi bigaturitsa umutima
Ukaba mumaganya wambaza umukama
Nico gituma benshi bamwe baba abasuma
Ukama wifuza kubivamo bikakubera ingome
Ukamera imvi mbere yuko umera umusatsi
Impfuvyi niyo kwitaho siyo gutera ibyatsi
Urayikubita hamwe uyirekere amayira
Uyime utayitutse kuko nayo aho ibaye
Nawe wari kuyitahura
Erega kuva kera burya siko vyahora
Atari ibintu byubu byamaze kuyangara

Kera ntiyaruwumwe ahubwo bwari ubumwe
Kandi baranatahura yuko ari bamwe
Umwana wese bakamurera co kimwe
Ariko ubu ntibakibyumva co kimwe
Ubu arahwera ntibamufashe nakimwe
Yahora yari uwâ€™ u Burundi ubu yabaye uwi kirere
Ntagira kirera ntiyize ahubwo yabaye ikirere
Yirirwa munzira abandi bari mu ishuri
Uronka abakurerera nawe raba umurere
Ivyâ€™umuntu nubundi ntukavyibagire aah
Zirisha mpanda ziraririye mukike
Burya hazoteba hagere
Igihe wafashe urugendo rwagasaga mwâ€™isi ya gacerere
Aaahh

[Yvette]

Siko yari ahubwo niko yabaye
Yavutse nk'abandi arira agahozwa
Bwarakeye bucana ayandi
Aho yariraha barabahamba
Kiramwa kira kandi cagutse
Yabaye impfuvyi atabishaka

[B Face]

Yoo reka mbabwire
Harya uwutazi ivyisi azokwama
Avyita ivyiwe
Fasha abandi ukibishoboye
Kuko twese turi abahita
mpore mwana mpore kibondo
Uri impfuvyi nturi igipfu  
Uko bukeye siko bwira
Kandi nta mvura idahita
Yoo buri wese akore icyo ashoboye
Kugirango umwana wimpfuvyi
Cangwa uwo mwibarabara abeho nkabandi
Nkuko n'amashyirahamwe afasha abana
Asanzwe abikora Imana niyo izobiguhembera
Yoo Yvette hoza uwo mwana twigire.
